# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository regardless of the committer's local git
# config (Windows' core.autocrlf commonly defaults to true, converting on checkout/commit
# and causing noisy whole-file diffs). The bot runs on Linux in production, so LF is the
# canonical form; this makes checkouts consistent across platforms.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
